    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows some minor signs of use, including a few light rock chips and small surface scratches consistent with its age, but it still maintains a great overall appearance. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, reflecting careful ownership. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
